; Coverage for report.cc fn_commodity_price
; Looks up the price of a commodity at a given date via the price history

P 2024/01/01 AAPL $150.00
P 2024/02/01 AAPL $160.00

2024/01/15 Buy
    Assets:Stocks    10 AAPL
    Assets:Cash     $-1500.00

; commodity_price returns the price at the given date
test reg --format '%(commodity_price(amount, date))\n' Assets:Stocks
$150.00
end test
